    </div>


                        

                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 content  ">
                        <h3>Combined dental agreement</h3>
<p>The 'Service agreement for the provision of oral health services for adolescents and special dental services for children and adolescents' is commonly known as the 'Combined dental agreement' or the CDA.</p>
<p>The current CDA took effect on 1 November 2025.</p>
<p><a class="download-block-link btn-external-custom btn" href="https://static.info.content.health.nz/docs/health-pros/topics/nationwide-service-framework/oh/Combined-Dental-Agreement-1-Nov-25-to-20-June-2026.pdf" data-type="pdf" data-size="418 KB">Combined dental agreement</a></p>
<h3>Operational guidelines</h3>
<p>These guidelines took effect 1 November 2025.</p>
<p><a class="download-block-link btn-external-custom btn" href="https://static.info.content.health.nz/docs/health-pros/topics/nationwide-service-framework/oh/Operational-Guidelines-for-the-Combined-Dental-Agreement.pdf" data-type="pdf" data-size="1.2 MB">Operational guidelines for the combined dental agreement</a></p>
<h3>License to occupy</h3>
<p>The Ministry of Education 'Licence to occupy' is for CDA contractors using school premises to provide adolescent dental services.</p>
<p><a class="download-block-link btn-external-custom btn" href="https://static.info.content.health.nz/docs/health-pros/topics/nationwide-service-framework/oh/licensetooccupy.doc" data-type="doc" data-size="95 KB">Licence to occupy school premises</a></p>
<h3>Back-to-back agreement for mobile providers</h3>
<p><a class="download-block-link btn-external-custom btn" href="https://static.info.content.health.nz/docs/health-pros/topics/nationwide-service-framework/oh/03_back_to_back_agreement_-_mobile_dental_providers.pdf" data-type="pdf" data-size="185 KB">Sub-contracting agreement for oral health services for adolescents</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>



	</div>


            
        
    


            
